* Dinobot watched the screen intently until suddenly there was a voice 
beside him, he snarled menacingly and turned towards the source of the 
sound. Tavatron!
He glared at her for a moment then went back to monitoring the screen, he 
didn't like it when quiet walking bots got the drop on him!
The computer screen was overflowing with the past few solar-cycles of 
Predacon activity, but none of it had anything to do with the upcoming 
attack.
Dinobot growled and tapped his raptor claw against the table's surface, 
there was nothing there but records about who entered the Pred base and who 
left.
His tail twitched, there was nothing of any real importance there!*

" Nothing...of importance."
